com.udeyrishi.androidelasticsearchdatamanager

Class DataKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.udeyrishi.androidelasticsearchdatamanager.DataKey

  • public class DataKey
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that acts as the key mapping to an object being stored by a DataManager. Behaviourally, this key should correspond to the path where an object is stored. The particulars of the correspondence may be determined by the implementations of DataManager. Created by rishi on 15-10-29.
